  "instructions": [
    "Dry rinse katsuramuki greens and pat them dry with a towel.",
    "Toss the greens with 5 ml olive oil, lemon juice, sea salt and freshly ground pepper until evenly coated.",
    "Sprinkle grated parmesan and chopped mint over the salad and gently fold to combine.",
    "Drizzle clotted cream over the salad to create a velvety coating and fold again.",
    "Sprinkle toasted sunflower seeds on top for a crunchy contrast.",
    "Let the salad sit for 5 minutes to allow flavors to meld.",
    "Serve immediately on a chilled platter.",
    "Garnish with extra pepper and a drizzle of olive oil if desired."
  ],
